            <a href="/legal/terms-and-conditions?updated=true&amp;lang=en">
                <span>OpenTable Terms of Use
                </span>
            </a>
        </span>
        <span lang=EN-US>) you purchase through our Sites, and social networks that you use in connection with our Sites) may also collect,
            use, and share information about you. This Policy does not cover such third parties or their services and we
            do not take any responsibility for how such third parties may use any information they collect. For information
            about third-party privacy practices, please consult with them directly.</span>
