        </span>
    </p>

    <p class=MsoNormal>
        <span lang=EN-US>
            <o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>
        </span>
    </p>

    <p class=MsoNormal>
        <b>
            <span lang=EN-US>Text Messages.</span>
        </b>
        <b>
            <span lang=EN-US> </span>
        </b>
        <span lang=EN-US>If you no longer want to receive text messages from OpenTable, reply <b>STOP</b> (or as otherwise instructed) in the text
            message. </span>
        <span lang=EN-US>
            <span> </span>If you have an OpenTable account, you may also adjust your account settings to opt-out of text messages.</span>
        <span
            lang=EN-US> Alternatively, to the extent that applicable law requires your prior opt-in consent to receive text messages, you
            can choose not to opt-in.</span>
            <span lang=EN-US>
                <o:p></o:p>
            </span>
    </p>

    <p class=MsoNormal>
        <b>
            <span lang=EN-US>
                <o:p>&nbsp;</o:p>
            </span>
        </b>
