        <span lang=EN-US> </span>
        <span lang=EN-US>section, above, we may collect information about your location if you enable location services through the settings
            in your mobile device, or, as required, with your consent. You can change the privacy settings of your device
            at any time to turn off the sharing of this location information with our Sites. If you choose to turn off location
            services, this could affect certain features or services of our Sites. If you have specific questions about the
            privacy settings of your device, we suggest you contact the manufacturer of your device or your mobile service
